Package: rms
Title: CMHC Rental Market Survey Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "McManus", , "tmcmanus@blueprint-ade.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: `rms` packages Rental Market Survey RMS data from CMHC for convenient access in R.
  Currently supports Rental Market Report data from 2018 to 2023. 
